channel.description: [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/2hoxllh.png[/img] New-World is a old scool classic pi that you cant find these days. We have most skills, and are adding quest. Our development thread is here: [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,566899.0.html]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,566899.0.html[/url] We are in need of more help, as we want this server to be released as soon as possible and have weekly updates. You can apply for server developer, client developer, or web developer Format to join [code]Name: Age: Applying For: Experience: How active will you be: Skype:[/code]
